5 March 2013The South African Chapter of the SADC Media awards has launched the 2013 Media Awards Competition which is open to all journalists who are South African nationals. The Award is in the fields of print journalism, radio journalism, television journalism and photojournalism.Entries to be submitted to Chairperson: National Adjudication Committee (NAC) Ms Zingisa Mkhuma C/O The Star 47 Sauer Street Johannesburg 2000 More information The National Adjudication Committee (NAC) Chair: Ms Zingisa Mkhuma Tel: 0796548458 The SADC shall not be responsible for any loss or damage to the work or material submitted.